---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  titleSv="Vad vi gör — Sigvardsson Consulting Group"
  titleEn="What We Do — Sigvardsson Consulting Group"
  descriptionSv="Tre pelare som driver vår leverans: vi identifierar utmaningen, skapar projektet och bygger processen för bestående förändring."
  descriptionEn="Three pillars that drive our delivery: we identify the challenge, create the project and build the process for lasting change."
  canonical="https://www.sigvardsson.org/what-we-do/"
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label sv-text">Vad vi gör</span>
      <span class="section-label en-text">What We Do</span>
      <h1>
        <span class="sv-text">Tre pelare.<br/>Bestående resultat.</span>
        <span class="en-text">Three pillars.<br/>Lasting results.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub sv-text">Vår leveransmodell bygger på att identifiera rätt utmaning, genomföra rätt projekt och bygga rätt process — i den ordningen, alltid.</p>
      <p class="hero-sub en-text">Our delivery model is built on identifying the right challenge, executing the right project and building the right process — in that order, always.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pillars">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up">
        <div class="pillar-number">01</div>
        <div class="pillar-content">
          <h2 class="sv-text">Utmaningen</h2>
          <h2 class="en-text">The Challenge</h2>
          <p class="sv-text">Vi börjar alltid med att förstå din verkliga utmaning. Inte symptomen — utan grundorsaken. Genom djupgående analys av data, processer och organisation kartlägger vi var den verkliga förbättringspotentialen finns.</p>
          <p class="en-text">We always start by understanding your real challenge. Not the symptoms — but the root cause. Through in-depth analysis of data, processes and organization, we map out where the real improvement potential lies.</p>
          <ul class="pillar-list">
            <li class="sv-text">Affärsanalys och datakartläggning</li>
            <li class="en-text">Business analysis and data mapping</li>
            <li class="sv-text">Identifiering av förbättringsområden</li>
            <li class="en-text">Identification of improvement areas</li>
            <li class="sv-text">Prioritering av initiativ med högst ROI</li>
            <li class="en-text">Prioritization of initiatives with highest ROI</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card fade-up">
        <div class="pillar-number">02</div>
        <div class="pillar-content">
          <h2 class="sv-text">Projektet</h2>
          <h2 class="en-text">The Project</h2>
          <p class="sv-text">Vi genomför varje projekt med tydliga mål, ansvar och tidplaner. Mobil-first, datadrivet och med fokus på omedelbar effekt. Varje projekt levererar mätbar ROI — från dag ett.</p>
          <p class="en-text">We execute every project with clear goals, accountability and timelines. Mobile-first, data-driven and focused on immediate impact. Every project delivers measurable ROI — from day one.</p>
          <ul class="pillar-list">
            <li class="sv-text">Tydlig projektplan och milstolpar</li>
            <li class="en-text">Clear project plan and milestones</li>
            <li class="sv-text">Hands-on genomförande med ditt team</li>
            <li class="en-text">Hands-on execution with your team</li>
            <li class="sv-text">Kontinuerlig mätning och justering</li>
            <li class="en-text">Continuous measurement and adjustment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card fade-up">
        <div class="pillar-number">03</div>
        <div class="pillar-content">
          <h2 class="sv-text">Processen</h2>
          <h2 class="en-text">The Process</h2>
          <p class="sv-text">Vi bygger inte bara resultat — vi bygger förmåga. Genom att involvera hela din organisation och skapa strukturerade processer säkerställer vi att förändringen håller långsiktigt.</p>
          <p class="en-text">We don't just build results — we build capability. By involving your entire organization and creating structured processes, we ensure that the change lasts long-term.</p>
          <ul class="pillar-list">
            <li class="sv-text">Processdokumentation och rutiner</li>
            <li class="en-text">Process documentation and routines</li>
            <li class="sv-text">Utbildning och kompetensöverföring</li>
            <li class="en-text">Training and knowledge transfer</li>
            <li class="sv-text">Uppföljningssystem och KPI:er</li>
            <li class="en-text">Follow-up systems and KPIs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="wwd-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner fade-up">
        <h2>
          <span class="sv-text">Nyfiken på hur vi kan hjälpa dig?</span>
          <span class="en-text">Curious how we can help you?</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-light sv-text">Se alla tjänster</a>
          <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-light en-text">See all services</a>
          <a href="/Contact/" class="btn btn-outline sv-text">Kontakta oss</a>
          <a href="/Contact/" class="btn btn-outline en-text">Contact us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-blue) 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .page-hero .section-label { color: var(--color-blue-lite); }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .pillars {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(1,13,96,0.08);
  }

  .pillar-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .pillar-number {
    font-family: 'Chakra Petch', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-blue-lite);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .pillar-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pillar-content p {
    color: rgba(1,13,96,0.7);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .pillar-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-navy-mid);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pillar-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-blue-lite);
  }

  .wwd-cta {
    background: var(--color-navy);
    padding: 4.5rem 2rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-light {
    background: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    font-family: 'Chakra Petch', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-light:hover { background: var(--color-off-white); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    font-family: 'Chakra Petch', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); color: var(--color-white); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .pillar-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .pillar-number { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
